Eng:
Hello World,

Here is my first map ze_ whose theme Halo.
This is the 1st beta. The RAD is not enabled on this version.
The 1st part of the map should contain displacements on the cliffs
but due to some problems I do for the next version.
The insctructions are in French. I'll try to translate them into English for the next version.
The map was not yet tested on a zombie mod server
You must have NoBlock on your server for this map

Bonjour à tous,
